{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MzE1Ng_0009", "text": "做個規矩的愛人 要完全純潔 良心太多負荷", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 18}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 3, 9, 3, 4, 0, 4, 0, 0, 0, 4, 0, 3, 4, 3, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zou6", "go3", "kwai1", "geoi2", "dik1", "oi3", "jan4", "jiu3", "jyun4", "cyun4", "seon4", "git3", "loeng4", "sam1", "taai3", "do1", "fu6", "ho4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "做個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "規矩", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "完全", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "純潔", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "良心", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "負荷", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "爲非作歹", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3156", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MzE1Ng_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MzE1Ng_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MzE1Ng_0010", "text": "爲了討好一個人 理智隨時矇蔽 爲非作歹是我", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 19}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 9, 9, 3, 4, 0, 5, 4, 0, 0, 0, 4, 3, 4, 9, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["liu5", "tou2", "hou2", "jat1", "go3", "jan4", "lei5", "zi3", "ceoi4", "si4", "mung4", "bai3", "fei1", "zok3", "daai2", "si6", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "爲了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "討好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "理智", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "隨時", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "矇蔽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲非作歹", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "爲非作歹", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3156", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MzE1Ng_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MzE1Ng_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MzE1Ng_0011", "text": "但我始終執迷 也從來無悔 顧不了這麼多", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 9, 3, 3, 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 4, 4, 3, 5, 5, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "ngo5", "ci2", "zung1", "zap1", "mai4", "jaa5", "cung4", "loi4", "mou4", "fui3", "gu3", "bat1", "liu5", "ze5", "mo1", "do1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "始終", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "執迷", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "從來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無悔", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "顧不了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "爲非作歹", "artists": ["王菲"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3156", "prev_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MzE1Ng_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_546L6I-y_MzE1Ng_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
